short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Keybank is an embedded payment terminal that enhances the productivity and functionality of QuickBooks Online.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Easily send payment links via email or text directly from QuickBooks Online, utilizing a KeyBank Merchant Account.

Help Save Money
KeyBank for QuickBooks Online helps users save money by embedding a KeyBank Merchant Account. Get paid without leaving QuickBooks or changing existing processes.

Help Save Time
Provide multiple frictionless payment options and a 24x7 self-service Customer Portal. All payments reconcile to Invoices following GAAP standards. No more chasing payments, manual processes, double entry, or reconciliation.

Help Increase Cashflow 
Email or text payment links to multiple Customers and set automated reminders. KeyBank reduces Invoice-to-cash time by 40% on average. Never stress over paying vendors or making payroll again.

Banking products and services are offered by KeyBank National Association. All merchant services, credit, and leasing products are subject to credit approval, terms of service, and any applicable collateral requirement(s).
